The following positions and units are included within the Department:
The Maryland Agricultural Fair Board;
The Chief of Weights and Measures;
The State Chemist;
The State Veterinarian;
The State Board of Veterinary Medical Examiners;
The State Soil Conservation Committee;
The Board of Review of the Department of Agriculture;
The Maryland Agricultural Commission;
The Maryland Horse Industry Board; and
The Maryland Winery and Grape Growers' Advisory Board.
